513	### 5.7. DebtAgingReportService — Aging Logic
514	
515	```php
516	class DebtAgingReportService
517	{
518	    /**
519	     * agingReport() — Báo cáo tuổi nợ
520	     *
521	     * Buckets: current (chưa đến hạn), 1-30, 31-60, 61-90, >90 ngày
522	     *
523	     * Query:
524	     * SELECT
525	     *   c.id as customer_id, c.customer_name,
526	     *   SUM(CASE WHEN i.due_date >= CURDATE() THEN i.outstanding ELSE 0 END) as current_bucket,
527	     *   SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), i.due_date) BETWEEN 1 AND 30 THEN i.outstanding ELSE 0 END) as bucket_1_30,
528	     *   SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), i.due_date) BETWEEN 31 AND 60 THEN i.outstanding ELSE 0 END) as bucket_31_60,
529	     *   SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), i.due_date) BETWEEN 61 AND 90 THEN i.outstanding ELSE 0 END) as bucket_61_90,
530	     *   SUM(CASE WHEN DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), i.due_date) > 90 THEN i.outstanding ELSE 0 END) as bucket_over_90,
531	     *   SUM(i.outstanding) as total_outstanding
532	     * FROM invoices i
533	     * JOIN customers c ON c.id = i.customer_id
534	     * WHERE i.status NOT IN ('PAID','CANCELLED','VOID','DRAFT')
535	     *   AND i.outstanding > 0
536	     *   AND i.deleted_at IS NULL
537	     * GROUP BY c.id, c.customer_name
538	     * ORDER BY total_outstanding DESC
539	     *
540	     * Performance: Sử dụng GENERATED COLUMN `outstanding` (STORED) → index-friendly
541	     */
542	    public function agingReport(Request $request): array
543	
544	    /**
545	     * debtTrend() — Xu hướng công nợ 6 tháng
546	     *
547	     * Mỗi tháng: tổng outstanding tại cuối tháng
548	     * Logic: snapshot-based hoặc point-in-time calculation
549	     */
550	    public function debtTrend(Request $request): array
551	}
